OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,FRussell Findlay has promised to cut
OL,8,Ftaxes permanently for businesses in
OL,9,FScotland if his party wins the
OL,10,FHolyrood election.
OL,12,FThe Scottish Conservative leader
OL,13,Fpledged to overhaul business rates and
OL,14,Freverse what his party described as
OL,15,F"damaging cliff-edge" tax rises set
OL,16,Ffor this April.
OL,18,FUnder his plans, properties valued
OL,19,Funder #20,000 would pay no tax at all.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774933457
OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,FFor higher-valued premises, businesses
OL,8,Fwould pay tax only above the #20,000
OL,9,Fthreshold, with the same principle
OL,10,Fapplied each time a property enters a
OL,11,Fhigher tax band.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of a Confederation of
OL,14,FBritish Industry roundtable event in
OL,15,FEdinburgh, Mr Findlay said Scottish
OL,16,Fbusinesses were over-taxed and that he
OL,17,Fwas committed to growing the country's
OL,18,Feconomy and creating more jobs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
