CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774933457
OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,FThe Scottish Conservative manifesto
OL,8,Fhas pledged to end "extreme" business
OL,9,Frates by capping the maximum rise that
OL,10,Fcan happen each cycle.
OL,12,FIt comes as the Scottish Retail
OL,13,FConsortium (SRC) warned that medium
OL,14,Fand larger shops in Scotland will pay
OL,15,F#162 million more than their English
OL,16,Fcounterparts over the next three years.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
