CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774933457
OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,FThe Tories have also promised to
OL,8,Fintroduce a new Bill in partnership
OL,9,Fwith businesses that would allow them
OL,10,Fto apply for regulations to be
OL,11,Fscrapped or amended, with a final
OL,12,Fdecision resting with ministers.
OL,14,FThe party also wants to establish
OL,15,FCanary Wharf-style enterprise zones
OL,16,Fwhere councils or ministers could
OL,17,Fstreamline planning rules, provide tax
OL,18,Fbreaks and acquire land to invest in
OL,19,Fdeclining parts of the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
