CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774933457
OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,FThe Conservative manifesto will also
OL,8,Fcommit to using Apprenticeship Levy
OL,9,Ffunding paid by businesses to set up a
OL,10,Fnew fund that would increase support
OL,11,Ffor apprenticeships and be demand-led.
OL,13,FMr Findlay said: "As the party of
OL,14,Fbusiness, the Scottish Conservatives
OL,15,Fare committed to creating a positive
OL,16,Fenvironment for firms to thrive `
OL,17,Fwhich would create jobs and increase
OL,18,Fprosperity.
OL,26,@uD@ROU
