OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774933457
OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,F"Scottish businesses and workers are
OL,8,Fbeing relentlessly hammered by SNP and
OL,9,FLabour taxes.
OL,11,F"My party would fundamentally overhaul
OL,12,FScotland's business rates system to
OL,13,Fmake them fair and transparent.
OL,15,F"We'd also work with business to cut
OL,16,Fcostly red tape and ensure that
OL,17,Fapprenticeships are properly funded
OL,18,Fafter being short-changed by the SNP.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
