OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774933457
OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,F"An SNP majority would be a disaster
OL,8,Ffor Scotland's economy, but voters can
OL,9,Fstop this nightmare scenario by
OL,10,Fbacking the Scottish Conservatives on
OL,11,Ftheir peach ballot paper."
OL,13,FThe SRC has also been campaigning for
OL,14,Freforms to the way businesses in
OL,15,FScotland are taxed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@ZO]
