OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,FThe industry body welcomed the
OL,8,FScottish Government's rates relief for
OL,9,Fsmaller retail, hospitality and
OL,10,Fleisure firms but said it was still
OL,11,Flower than the levels seen in England,
OL,12,Fwhere they are uncapped.
OL,14,FAnd it said there was no such relief
OL,15,Ffor the more than 2,000 premises in
OL,16,FScotland with a rateable value of more
OL,17,Fthan #100,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
