CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774933457
OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,FThese shops will pay the higher rate
OL,8,Fof 54.8p in the pound from April 1 `
OL,9,Ffar above the 43p rate in England. The
OL,10,FSRC said Scots firms were paying #54
OL,11,Fmillion a year more than those down
OL,12,Fsouth, or #162 million over the three-
OL,13,Fyear rates period.
OL,15,FDavid Lonsdale, director of the SRC,
OL,16,Fsaid: "As it stands, Scotland risks
OL,17,Fbecoming a materially less competitive
OL,18,Fplace to operate shops and our fear is
OL,19,Fthis could see a shift in investment
OL,20,Fdown south.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
