OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774933457
OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,F"Continued investment in stores is
OL,8,Fessential to keep them viable and
OL,9,Fattractive to customers and to
OL,10,Fminimise the number of shuttered shops.
OL,12,F"It is not in the interests of
OL,13,FScotland's economy for shop owners to
OL,14,Fbe incentivised to invest in Berwick-
OL,15,Fupon-Tweed over Bothwell, Buckhaven,
OL,16,For Blairgowrie.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
