OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,F"A far more ambitious approach is
OL,8,Frequired from those political parties
OL,9,Fseeking to form the next Scottish
OL,10,FGovernment, one that at the very least
OL,11,Fensures a competitive level playing
OL,12,Ffield with England and which delivers
OL,13,Fon the industry's vision to make
OL,14,FScotland the best place in the UK to
OL,15,Fgrow a retail business."
