OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,FCalum Kerr, SNP candidate for
OL,8,FMidlothian South, Tweeddale &
OL,9,FLauderdale, said: "John Swinney's
OL,10,Fstrong leadership is firmly on the
OL,11,Fside of Scottish business ` with
OL,12,FLabour's hike to employer's national
OL,13,Finsurance and rising energy bills
OL,14,Fruining jobs, our range of rates
OL,15,Freliefs is a lifeline for many.
