OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,F"We've lifted 100,000 businesses out
OL,8,Fof rates, GDP figures show we
OL,9,Foutperformed the UK, Scotland has the
OL,10,Fhighest levels of foreign direct
OL,11,Finvestment outside of London and two
OL,12,Fglobal credit rating agencies have
OL,13,Fgiven Scotland a high investment grade
OL,14,F` that's what you get with an SNP
OL,15,Fgovernment on Scotland's side.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
