OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,F"Russell Findlay backed Liz Truss
OL,8,Fevery step of the way as she wrecked
OL,9,Fthe economy while the Tories'
OL,10,Fdisastrous Brexit has hammered
OL,11,FScottish business ` that's the reality
OL,12,Fof Westminster and, through a fresh
OL,13,Fstart with independence, we can escape
OL,14,Fthat broken system for good."
