OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,FScottish Liberal Democrat finance and
OL,8,Feconomy spokesperson Jamie Greene MSP
OL,9,Fsaid: "The Tories like to talk the big
OL,10,Ftalk on business, but when it comes
OL,11,Fdown to it, the Lib Dems actually get
OL,12,Fstuff done for Scotland's hard-pressed
OL,13,FSMEs.
OL,15,F"When they had the chance to ease the
OL,16,Fpressures felt by businesses because
OL,17,Fof crushing rates rises, the Scottish
OL,18,FTories simply shouted from the
OL,19,Fsidelines.
OL,26,@qD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
