SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774933457
OL,3,CFindlay promises permanent tax cuts
OL,4,Cfor business and Scottish 'Canary
OL,5,CWharf'
OL,7,F"They never had a seat at the
OL,8,Fnegotiating table because they choose
OL,9,Fto play party politics over pragmatism.
OL,11,F"By contrast, I used those budget
OL,12,Fnegotiations as leverage to squeeze
OL,13,Fthe SNP for every penny I could and,
OL,14,Fas a result, secured #178 million in
OL,15,Frates relief for pubs, clubs,
OL,16,Frestaurants, hotels and self-caterers.
OL,18,F"The Tories got nothing, they didn't
OL,19,Feven try.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
